'''玛丽安·奥尔'''（{{lang-en|Marian Orr}}，{{bd|1970年||}}）是[[美国|美国]]政治家，现任[[怀俄明州|怀俄明州]][[夏延_(怀俄明州)|夏延市]]市长，也是該市首位女市長。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cheyennecity.org/1572/Biography|title=Biography {{!}} Cheyenne, WY - Official Website|website=www.cheyennecity.org|access-date=2019-08-17|archive-date=2020-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200614125342/https://www.cheyennecity.org/1572/Biography|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="#1">{{Cite web|url=https://apnews.com/f28f9d094e844ee1b69380290c2c9e93|title=Wyoming mayor: Governor cursed, slammed fists in meeting|last=Gruver|first=Mead|date=2019-06-03|website=AP NEWS|access-date=2019-08-17|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127204312/https://apnews.com/f28f9d094e844ee1b69380290c2c9e93|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.wyomingpublicmedia.org/post/two-women-vie-become-cheyennes-first-female-mayor|title=Two Women Vie To Become Cheyenne's First Female Mayor|last=Ballard|first=Caroline|website=www.wyomingpublicmedia.org|language=en|access-date=2019-08-17|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926065422/https://www.wyomingpublicmedia.org/post/two-women-vie-become-cheyennes-first-female-mayor|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 早年生活 ==
奥尔于1992年毕业于[[怀俄明大学|怀俄明大学]]，获得传播学学位。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.uwyo.edu/uwyo/2017/18-3/alumnews/cheyennes-first-female-mayor.html|title=Cheyenne's First Female Mayor {{!}} April 2017 {{!}} Vol. 18, No. 3|website=www.uwyo.edu|access-date=2019-08-17|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809172746/http://www.uwyo.edu/uwyo/2017/18-3/alumnews/cheyennes-first-female-mayor.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
== 生涯 ==
2016年，她以56%的选票当选夏延市市长。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.wyomingpublicmedia.org/post/marian-orr-wins-cheyenne-mayoral-race|title=Marian Orr Wins Cheyenne Mayoral Race|last=Ballard|first=Caroline|website=www.wyomingpublicmedia.org|language=en|access-date=2019-08-17|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116003052/https://www.wyomingpublicmedia.org/post/marian-orr-wins-cheyenne-mayoral-race|dead-url=no}}</ref>
=== 马克·戈登争议 ===
奥尔会见[[怀俄明州州长|怀俄明州州长]]马克·戈登时受到了全国的报道，当时一个[[台湾|台湾]]代表团提议对她进行访问。她指责他骂她说“去你的，市长”，并“使用攻击性和威胁性的肢体语言”。<ref name="#1"/>戈登本来想取消这次访问，但奥尔提议继续访问。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3019417/president-tsai-ing-wens-high-profile-us-visits-keep-taiwan|title=Tsai's US visits keep Taiwan in spotlight and send message to Beijing|date=2019-07-20|website=South China Morning Post|language=en|access-date=2019-08-17|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122031627/https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3019417/president-tsai-ing-wens-high-profile-us-visits-keep-taiwan|dead-url=no}}</ref>戈登打电话给奥尔，为他的言语道歉，但公开表示，她对奥尔身体行为的说法是错误的。<ref name="#1"/><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.washingtonexaminer.com/news/wyoming-governor-accused-of-screaming-f-you-mayor-at-female-republican|title=Wyoming governor accused of screaming "F--k you, mayor" at female Republican|date=2019-06-04|website=Washington Examiner|language=en|access-date=2019-08-17|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126201417/https://www.washingtonexaminer.com/news/wyoming-governor-accused-of-screaming-f-you-mayor-at-female-republican|dead-url=no}}</ref>奥尔表示，她觉得自己必须公开州长的行为的原因是，“我们不能对男性那样对待女性的不良行为保持沉默，这是不可接受的。”<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.wyomingpublicmedia.org/post/cheyenne-mayor-accuses-governor-intimidating-behavior|title=Cheyenne Mayor Accuses Governor Of Intimidating Behavior|last=Beck|first=Bob|website=www.wyomingpublicmedia.org|language=en|access-date=2019-08-17|archive-date=2019-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190817154647/https://www.wyomingpublicmedia.org/post/cheyenne-mayor-accuses-governor-intimidating-behavior|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 个人生活 ==
她的丈夫是记者吉米·奥尔，后者在2001年至2004年担任白宫互联网总监。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://georgewbush-whitehouse.archives.gov/government/text/orr-bio.html|title=Jimmy Orr, White House Internet Director, 2001-2004 (Text Only)|website=georgewbush-whitehouse.archives.gov|access-date=2019-08-17|archive-date=2021-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210330182724/https://georgewbush-whitehouse.archives.gov/government/text/orr-bio.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年12月20日，奥尔的丈夫因涉嫌对她实施家庭暴力而被捕。截至2019年12月24日，他已被从拉勒米县监狱释放，并被控犯有家庭暴力罪。作为保释的条件，他不能与她有任何联系，也不能进入他们住所附近的街区。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.laramieboomerang.com/news/cheyenne-mayor-s-husband-pleads-not-guilty-to-domestic-battery/article_3ffa7651-c7e7-5799-b51d-1bd90b2239b3.html|title=Cheyenne mayor's husband pleads not guilty to domestic battery charge|access-date=2021-01-18|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124160117/https://www.laramieboomerang.com/news/cheyenne-mayor-s-husband-pleads-not-guilty-to-domestic-battery/article_3ffa7651-c7e7-5799-b51d-1bd90b2239b3.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

